text: Harvinder Kalyan is an Indian politician. He belongs to Ror community. He was elected to the Haryana Legislative Assembly from Gharaunda in the 2014, 2019 and 2024 Haryana Legislative Assembly election as a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. == References == Category:Indian politicians Category:1967 births Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians
title: Harvinder Kalyan
